OL,3,CNew #1.5m Scottish Dark Sky
OL,4,CObservatory to boost south of Scotland
OL,5,Ctourism
OL,7,FA new home has been found for the
OL,8,FScottish Dark Sky Observatory, three
OL,9,Fyears after it was destroyed by fire
OL,10,Fin the Galloway Forest Park.
OL,12,FThe new national astronomical
OL,13,Fobservatory will be located at
OL,14,FClatteringshaws Loch within the
OL,15,FGalloway Forest Park.
OL,17,FThe observatory is expected to open in
OL,18,Flate 2026 following a #1.5m
OL,19,Fredevelopment, creating a number of
OL,20,Fjobs and volunteering positions.
