OL,5,Ctourism
OL,7,FProposed plans for the new observatory
OL,8,Fwill see two observing domes, each
OL,9,Ffeaturing a large telescope, and a
OL,10,F360 planetarium offering immersive
OL,11,Feducational shows and night-sky
OL,12,Fsimulations installed.
OL,14,FThe site, which was previously the
OL,15,FClatteringshaws Visitor Centre, was
OL,16,Fpurchased with the help of #200k of
OL,17,Fgrant funding from South of Scotland
OL,18,FEnterprise (SoSE) and support during
OL,19,Fthe process from the South of Scotland
OL,20,FDestination Alliance (SSDA).
