OL,7,FAnthony Daye, South of Scotland
OL,8,FEnterprise, said: "We are delighted to
OL,9,Fhave supported SDSO with the purchase
OL,10,Fof the site for its new astronomical
OL,11,Fobservatory. With the South of
OL,12,FScotland now the country's Natural
OL,13,FCapital Innovation Zone, and SOSE also
OL,14,Flaunching a new Space Strategy this
OL,15,Fyear, the development of an
OL,16,Fastronomical observatory is an example
OL,17,Fof how we can we use natural resources
OL,18,Ffor the benefit of the region.
