OL,5,Ctourism
OL,7,F"These opportunities extend to
OL,8,Ftourism, with the planned observatory
OL,9,Fadding another visitor offering to the
OL,10,Falready fantastic tourism sector we
OL,11,Fhave in the South of Scotland."
OL,13,FThe location was selected due to the
OL,14,Fexceptional quality of the dark night
OL,15,Fskies overhead and its accessibility,
OL,16,Fhelping more people experience
OL,17,FScotland's only Gold Tier Dark Sky
OL,18,FPark.
