OL,4,CObservatory to boost south of Scotland
OL,5,Ctourism
OL,7,FThe former observatory opened in 2012
OL,8,Fnear Dalmellington in Ayrshire on the
OL,9,Fedge of the Galloway Forest Park but
OL,10,Fwas destroyed in a fire on 23 June
OL,11,F2021. A return to the former site was
OL,12,Fruled out last year following a
OL,13,Ffeasibility study due to poor
OL,14,Faccessibility, lack of utilities and
OL,15,Fsecurity concerns.
