OL,5,Ctourism
OL,7,FMarc Charron, Chairman of The Scottish
OL,8,FDark Sky Observatory Board, said: "We
OL,9,Fare absolutely thrilled to have
OL,10,Fsecured the purchase of such a
OL,11,Fwonderful site on which to create a
OL,12,Fnew astronomical observatory.
OL,14,F"We are determined to create an
OL,15,Foutstanding facility that will inspire
OL,16,Fpeople for generations to come in the
OL,17,Fwonders to behold in a truly dark
OL,18,Fnight sky."
