OL,7,FThe park, which is based near
OL,8,FKircudbright, was designated as
OL,9,FEurope's first 'gold tier' Dark Sky
OL,10,FPark by the International Dark-Sky
OL,11,FAssociation in 2009. The area's
OL,12,Frelatively low population density and
OL,13,Flow levels of obtrusive artificial
OL,14,Flight made it an ideal location.
